Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.90,0:00:14.99,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}Dawn comes softer than a sleeping breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.66,0:00:23.00,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6\fad(0,0)}Your dream runs through the forest now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.00,0:00:29.96,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6\fad(0,200)}You wake up and stir to find the light
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.09,0:00:37.80,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}If you've lost it, I'll find it for you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.85,0:00:47.31,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6\fad(200,0)}It's hidden in our future
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:55.45,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}Now if we joined hands
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.95,0:01:03.16,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}we would go far away without letting go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.33,0:01:11.09,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}In the memory of a far off day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.38,0:01:17.93,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}the story of the blue country bloomed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.18,0:01:21.81,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}Shining eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.93,0:01:26.02,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6\fad(200,0)}Your singing voice
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.02,0:01:29.02,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6\fad(0,200)}Let's share it
