Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.27,0:02:16.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H575F66&\4c&H575F66&\pos(640,504)\blur3\1c&HCCD4DD&}Wolf and Playful Days
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.58,0:02:34.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:35.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.26,0:02:38.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is too nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.24,0:02:49.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll get by without freezing like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.94,0:02:52.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.10,0:02:59.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm cold, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.23,0:03:02.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to be heated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.36,0:03:04.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.07,0:03:09.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Burnt rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.19,0:03:12.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That looks like burnt rice you see floating in stews!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.72,0:03:33.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You said Renose has lots of different kinds of strong liquor, right? {You said there were several types of strong alcoholic drink in Renose, didn't you?}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.72,0:03:34.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:37.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll probably be fine even if we get held up by a blizzard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.39,0:03:40.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope one comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.04,0:03:42.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey hey. {Careful what you wish for.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.77,0:03:48.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.42,0:03:52.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Renose is famous for its lumber and furs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.91,0:03:54.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.14,0:03:57.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get upset if you see wolves pelts among those furs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.81,0:04:03.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"I get eaten by wolves,"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.71,0:04:06.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"but mice get eaten by me."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.37,0:04:15.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In our world, it's normal to hunt and be hunted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.97,0:04:17.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:22.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And even though you say that, humans are even more shocking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.93,0:04:26.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You buy and sell each other, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.84,0:04:28.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the slave trade?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.75,0:04:31.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's profitable and a necessary business.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.86,0:04:35.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In the same way you calmly talk about trading people,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.47,0:04:39.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,we have no feelings for those who are hunted. {Just as you can talk about it like that, we're apathetic to those who were hunted.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.67,0:04:45.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, when I was being hunted by another man, you got pretty worked up, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.06,0:04:48.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes I got worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.79,0:04:49.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.29,0:04:51.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't speak in monotone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.49,0:04:52.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.83,0:04:54.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.11,0:04:59.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.00,0:05:04.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.56,0:05:05.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.18,0:05:27.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They're fellow merchants. {lit: people of the same trade (as me)}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.17,0:05:31.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like it'll take a while to enter the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.41,0:05:34.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this like a temple courtyard? {Norg: monzenchi seems to be The area in front of a temple which is officially inside the grounds of the temple but has merchants selling stuff, profits of which go towards the upkeep of the temple. original definition: 寺の門前の地所。江戸時代、名目上寺院の境内であるが、ここに商家を建てさせて、その収入を寺院の費用に充てた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.84,0:05:37.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are in front of churches.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.81,0:05:41.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's odd that they're setting up right in front of the town walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.56,0:05:44.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't look like they're doing any business either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.53,0:05:47.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The gates aren't closed,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.27,0:05:49.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,so it doesn't appear to be a revolt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.31,0:05:55.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're expecting another battle here, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.24,0:05:57.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't particularly want one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.78,0:05:59.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that face?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.98,0:06:06.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that ever since you met me you've been caught up in a number of disputes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.44,0:06:10.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But there hasn't been a single time where I directly caused one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.21,0:06:14.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The first one...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.27,0:06:17.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that may have been partially my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.30,0:06:20.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was more because you were greedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.41,0:06:24.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The next one happened entirely because you got greedy and failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.06,0:06:27.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And the last one was because you got all worked up on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.51,0:06:28.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.79,0:06:31.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I do see where you're coming from, {Norg: fuck this fucking line, help me うっちゃん lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.27,0:06:34.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but I have trouble accepting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.75,0:06:38.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it's true you weren't the cause of all the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.65,0:06:42.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's natural for you to find it hard to accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.45,0:06:43.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.82,0:06:48.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You always measure me against your own standards,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.49,0:06:51.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,so you feel you're being manipulated by me.  {.... check}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.90,0:06:54.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.59,0:06:57.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.15,0:07:03.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you!{horo's fantasy xD <3}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.84,0:07:06.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're finally being honest with yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.55,0:07:14.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good, not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.80,0:07:16.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.86,0:07:21.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stew would be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.95,0:07:24.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.14,0:07:25.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It is pretty cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.53,0:07:27.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It depends on the price,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.31,0:07:32.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but it'd be nice to have something with a flour and butter base rather than one with cream. {where the heck did she learn what that tastes like?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.33,0:07:35.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That does sound good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.05,0:07:39.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There are times when the scent of milk beats wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.07,0:07:42.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The vegetables at this time of year are still especially good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.61,0:07:44.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Vegetables?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.39,0:07:50.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know the taste of black, tender chunks of beef floating in a milky white broth?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.00,0:07:54.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they do say that good things are poison to the eyes and tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.19,0:07:58.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not very fair for me, considering I wasn't able to have a meal for several hundred years.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.73,0:08:01.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll consult my purse first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.12,0:08:16.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an identification plaque that shows you're a traveling merchant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.55,0:08:24.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The townsfolk won't do business with outsiders unless they display this,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.29,0:08:26.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,so make sure you don't lose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.12,0:08:33.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh what,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.11,0:08:35.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,it's just a cheap wolf pelt. {death glare!}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.52,0:08:49.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I think it's the best thing in the whole world. {Of course even I don't think it's the best of all things...}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.83,0:08:54.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's a matter of the differences between species, not the quality of my tail! {there's gotta be a better way to say this... she means that a wolf's fur can only be so good compared to other animals, but not sure how to put this succinctly}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:55.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.62,0:08:59.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Between something that's at the lower end of a superior scale,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.63,0:09:02.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and something that's at the upper end of an inferior scale,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.38,0:09:05.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,you'd definitely commend the second one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.06,0:09:06.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.51,0:09:07.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.55,0:09:15.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,between a steward from a noble house with no fame, fortune or personality, and an ordinary citizen with all three,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.70,0:09:19.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,no matter which way you look at it, you'd commend the latter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.01,0:09:29.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Room or luggage?{Norg: I don't know what service he is offering in reference to 荷物. to keep hold of it? to carry it? >.<}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:31.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I need a room for two.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.04,0:09:34.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you prefer a warm room or a bright one?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.84,0:09:37.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a choice besides the warm room?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.37,0:09:41.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll take the horse to the stables.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.20,0:09:42.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you talk to the maste...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.45,0:09:46.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,the old man, he'll get a room for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.11,0:09:47.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.45,0:10:07.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Behave yourself now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.60,0:10:29.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Third floor, by the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.86,0:10:31.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, third floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.73,0:10:34.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,By the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.63,0:10:54.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's a splendid tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.67,0:10:56.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good, warm fur.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.88,0:11:01.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'll go dry your clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.37,0:11:03.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When that's done, we'll get onto the stew!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:17.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Traveling merchant identity plaque, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:21.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Strange things they've got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.48,0:11:45.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh crap! {MAZUI!} {YAH BABY YAAH!}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.76,0:11:55.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.04,0:12:06.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.99,0:12:08.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.56,0:12:47.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go maintain the furs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.62,0:12:49.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to make sure they fetch a good price.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,0:12:55.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're already too expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.86,0:12:59.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So much that you won't find any buyers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.81,0:13:02.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Has anyone bought you at this point?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:06.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh come on.{OH U}{I want to put that in but it would sound stupendously gay}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.40,0:13:17.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.96,0:13:18.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.02,0:13:27.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.21,0:13:30.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Gathering stories about you comes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.34,0:13:34.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stories about me, and about Yoitsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.71,0:13:39.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's find a chronicler first like I did in Kumerson.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.31,0:13:41.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave that to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.41,0:13:44.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You know the right channels.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.74,0:13:46.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.93,0:13:47.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.82,0:13:49.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know how to go about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.73,0:13:51.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So what do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.28,0:13:55.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a saying that goes:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.11,0:13:57.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"The man who knows the way does the work."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.40,0:14:01.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"The man who knows why that man works becomes his employer."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:03.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.75,0:14:07.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I know why you work so gallantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.33,0:14:09.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They used to say that a long time ago. {BACK IN THE DAY BABY. yeah we'll change that lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.47,0:14:13.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So if I'm your employer, I have to reward you somehow. {don't eat with your mouth full, vulgar girl}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.32,0:14:15.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Reward?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.05,0:14:16.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.00,0:14:17.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.20,0:14:19.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,isn't there something you want? { COMMENT BY FOTC: ホロかわゆいっ } {do it in the butt.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.69,0:14:25.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:30.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you're in a good mood, I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.16,0:14:33.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you treating me like a spoiled child?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.94,0:14:37.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,At least children listen when you scold them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:43.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, first let's go talk to the old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.78,0:14:46.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't look it, but he is the owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.77,0:14:48.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're coming, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.67,0:14:49.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.62,0:14:51.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you smack away my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.31,0:14:58.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I clap my hands now, will the magic spell disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.48,0:15:04.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, what have I been doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.40,0:15:05.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.97,0:15:08.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,this is the town of lumber and fur, Renose!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.28,0:15:11.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I must stock up on furs and be off to the next town!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.36,0:15:18.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a traveling, traveling merchant?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:23.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can judge the quality of furs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.94,0:15:26.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you do have good eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.24,0:15:29.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But what about judging the quality of people?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:33.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.46,0:15:36.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I am under an evil spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.39,0:15:42.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we mustn't clap out hands, so as to keep it intact.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.07,0:15:44.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But they've already been clapped once.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:46.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying it's already disappearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.58,0:15:47.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.84,0:15:51.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So could you recast it before the magic fades?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.50,0:15:59.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this? { COMMENT BY FOTC: これは、これは. }
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.98,0:16:03.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come now. We're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.48,0:16:08.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.98,0:16:12.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't surprising enough to make you so clumsy, was—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.07,0:16:15.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your spell was too strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.90,0:16:16.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,you fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.79,0:16:28.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So when are you going to start running amok?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.72,0:16:29.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.99,0:16:33.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe when you stop doing things like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.77,0:16:36.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You've developed quite a sharp wit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.02,0:16:39.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.53,0:16:42.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You really have become a smooth talker.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:44.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get someone to teach you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.28,0:16:45.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.54,0:16:47.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It just came to me at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:48.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,At the moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:51.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes me even happier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.21,0:16:55.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When I stop doing things, you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.11,0:17:03.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.81,0:17:05.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.09,0:17:08.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted me to care that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:13.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.58,0:17:16.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A chronicler?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.48,0:17:16.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.73,0:17:20.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Or just someone who knows the legends of the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.50,0:17:27.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a man called Rigolo who was a chronicler, {リゴロ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.42,0:17:30.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but unfortunately, he's currently in a fifty-man meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.77,0:17:32.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He won't meet with anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.75,0:17:34.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fifty-man meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.34,0:17:36.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see the town entrance?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.92,0:17:37.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.38,0:17:40.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Merchant-like people were gathered there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.45,0:17:44.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that have something to do with this fifty-man meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.95,0:17:49.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying there's some kind of problem in town?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.65,0:17:52.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The furs, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.78,0:17:53.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Furs?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.16,0:17:59.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Rigolo is the scribe for the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.77,0:18:06.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,For legends, old lady Bolter the tanner knows quite a bit. { ボルタ }
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.16,0:18:08.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Any others?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.58,0:18:09.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Others?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.98,0:18:11.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.77,0:18:14.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,the old geezer at the Latton company. { 叔父御 }
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.01,0:18:15.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.85,0:18:18.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In the heat of the summer year before last...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.17,0:18:21.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My God.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.69,0:18:23.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.72,0:18:30.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The legends of the town will only be found in books.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.45,0:18:38.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.08,0:18:42.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll have to have Rigolo show us the records.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.28,0:18:43.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.35,0:18:48.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The years weather even stone towers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.52,0:18:51.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And even the memories of men...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.74,0:18:54.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's frightening.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.93,0:19:10.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.76,0:19:11.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Want something to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.76,0:19:17.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You should build more vocabulary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.07,0:19:34.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.43,0:19:41.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She was surprised when she saw me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.81,0:19:44.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me, another animal?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.83,0:19:47.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't get that feeling,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.38,0:19:52.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but maybe that girl was taken aback by my beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.08,0:19:53.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.48,0:19:55.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.42,0:19:56.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.75,0:19:57.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.46,0:19:59.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.84,0:20:04.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of mutt are you, looking around at other women when I'm right beside you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.86,0:20:08.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't say things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.92,0:20:12.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's much cuter if you show it with your behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.33,0:20:17.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a fool, so you wouldn't know if I didn't say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.19,0:20:30.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.40,0:20:31.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.79,0:20:34.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Will it be difficult to meet this whatsisname man?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.40,0:20:37.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He said his name was Rigolo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.23,0:20:41.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's in a meeting, then talking to him will be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.86,0:20:45.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it does depend on his role at the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.33,0:20:49.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That face says you want to know the subject of this meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:50.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.01,0:20:57.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, you'll be wandering around until the meeting is over with absolutely no interest in what's happening?{Then, with absolutely no interest, you'll just fool around until said meeting is over?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.93,0:21:02.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't fool the eyes of the sage wolf Horo, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.80,0:21:06.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know what's happening in town so badly, I can't help myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.65,0:21:07.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And maybe—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.45,0:21:09.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"if possible, make a profit."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.72,0:21:22.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's enough to require these wooden plaques.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.76,0:21:25.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Something interesting is happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.18,0:21:27.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.14,0:21:29.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.76,0:21:33.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.77,0:21:35.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.85,0:21:39.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,First, how about the sights of this town,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.84,0:21:41.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,dear princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.00,0:21:43.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.21,0:21:46.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.45,0:21:47.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.36,0:21:48.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What shall we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.16,0:21:52.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember whether I really came here or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.21,0:21:56.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's changed a lot since then, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.52,0:21:58.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to the port.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.04,0:21:59.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The port?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.49,0:22:01.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that ships have become quite common recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.13,0:22:03.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite a sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.10,0:22:06.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ships, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.13,0:22:06.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.12,0:23:52.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Wolf and Enticing Traveler
