Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.07,0:22:32.78,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5\fad(200,200)}missed each other just before love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.29,0:22:38.87,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5\fad(200,200)}I want to tell you but I keep quiet
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.17,0:22:41.96,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5\fad(200,200)}Take me, take me
