Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.09,0:22:53.14,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5\fad(200,200)}If you climb the hill towards the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.55,0:22:59.48,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5\fad(200,200)}there flows the comet river
